description: Step out of the house and onto the beach. Twomey Court offers the best of coastal living in the heart of South Boston. Just across the street from Castle Island, this rarely available two-bed condo sits on the 2nd floor of an exceptionally maintained association. Great sunlight, hardwood floors, and a welcoming living room overlooking a beautifully landscaped courtyard await you. The eat-in kitchen features white cabinetry, gas cooking, and stone countertops. Both bedrooms are spacious, ideal for guests, roommates, or a home office. The bathroom includes a step-in shower and a window for natural light. Additional perks include heat and hot water included in the condo fee, a private storage locker in the basement, common laundry, bike rack, and first-come, first-served association parking (one space per unit). It's no wonder units in this sea breeze community rarely hit the market. This is your chance to live steps from the sand while still enjoying all the conveniences of city life.
